    10364 [label=<BlueOakCouncil: <B><FONT COLOR="/svg/darkred">Lead</FONT></B><BR />These licenses lack one or more essential elements of permissive open software<BR />licenses or impose unusually burdensome requirements. &#32;Many use unclear,<BR />jocular, or incomplete language.>
